
Ranger Help for: enemy bird
===========================

SUMMARY:
Choosing bird means your Ranger specializes against avian creatures:
hawks, ravens, eagles, vultures, giant birds, and other winged hunters.

This choice fits Rangers who watch the sky as much as the ground. It can
be useful across many terrains because birds migrate, nest, scavenge, and
hunt almost everywhere.

COMMAND:
  setenemy bird

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: enemy, setenemy and terrains
